Name            : Dalnairn

Historical Theme: 

Races           : Dark-dwarf

Religion        : Soirin

Language        : Runic

Currency        : Shards

Game Notes      : Dalnairn is located on the island
                  of Averath south of the main continent.
                  It is inhabited by dark-dwarves who
                  worship Alessandra in the Soirin faith.
                  As such, they value money, pride, 
                  gluttony and other ideas typically
                  frowned upon by more moderate ideologies.
            
Game History    : 
              
Classes         : Evoker, Fighter, Priest (Soirin), Rogue

